{"tid":1978924,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[突發］奧尼爾死咗","createTime":"2020-04-19T05:18:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-19T06:47:50.000Z","uid":149494,"like":7,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"80365890bf561714cc9fda39eb4bfdd68222d013","tid":1978924,"uid":149494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T05:18:30.000Z","msg":"在美國前總統喬治布殊任內擔任財長的奧尼爾（Paul O'Neill）周六因癌症逝世，享年84歲。<br />\n<br />\n奧尼爾的母校印第安納大學公布他的死訊，指他在匹茲堡與世長辭。校方讚揚他正直不阿，擁有以數據為本的決策能力，對公職有強大的承擔。<br />\n<br />\n奧尼爾在喬治布殊第一個任期的頭兩年擔任美國財長，後來在政策上與政府有分歧，於2002年12月被罷免。離開政府後，他為作家塞斯金德提供材料，協助塞斯金德撰寫著作《忠誠的代價：喬治布殊、白宮及奧尼爾的教育》（The Price of Loyalty: George W. Bush, the White House and the Education of Paul O'Neill），讓讀者得知喬治布殊政府鮮為人知的一面。<br />\n<br />\n塞斯金德說：「透過我的著作，他向全世界講出伊拉克沒有大殺傷力武器、切尼（前任副總統）奪權及喬治布殊無能的真相。他相信真相，正是這個原因令他丟官。他是真正的美國英雄。再見了老朋友。」<br />\n<br />\n奧尼爾遺下妻子、4個孩子、12名孫兒和15個曾孫。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hd.stheadline.com/amp/news/realtime/wo/1750173/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Famp%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fwo%2F1750173%2F&d=TvWZhBC8jRU6oyAzZT7RDs3u7Zzj2Sx3DhCMrptFZ9w%3D&h=683eeda5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Famp%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fwo%2F1750173%2F&h=26fc2a13\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hd.stheadline.com/amp/news/realtime/wo/1750173/</a>"},{"pid":"ef25a9d5232ccdefb8e6ca14cca79b09f8b96af8","tid":1978924,"uid":170281,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T05:21:44.000Z","msg":"嘩 好叻叻呀 諗住同名呃d人入黎睇 叻叻豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18bec4051eab686dff788edf6bdc97dd23adcdf7","tid":1978924,"uid":136271,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T05:22:39.000Z","msg":"以為籃球個個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"892a6c905eea7990610e55d488a1beadd3642f5d","tid":1978924,"uid":23923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T05:23:25.000Z","msg"